   {:e #blake3 "1ff4d981f7667eb9f446f9502b42725e25825921395d21e15c2bd281cc06480a" :a :task/description :v "BACKGROUND: The DDIS methodology (INV/ADR/NEG, 7-component F(S), witnesses, harvest/seed) is currently compiled into bilateral.rs constants. Per ADR-FOUNDATION-013, the policy must be datoms. This task creates the DDIS manifest: the first epistemological policy on the braid substrate. Future domains (research, compliance, agile) will create different manifests with the same schema.. APPROACH: (1) In bootstrap.rs or a new policy.rs, define fn ddis_policy_datoms(tx_id) -> Vec<Datom>. (2) Create 7 boundary entities: :policy/boundary-validation (source=:spec/*, target=:witness/*, weight=0.18), :policy/boundary-coverage (source=:spec/*, target=:impl/*, weight=0.18), :policy/boundary-drift (weight=0.18), :policy/boundary-harvest (weight=0.13), :policy/boundary-contradiction (weight=0.13), :policy/boundary-incompleteness (weight=0.08), :policy/boundary-uncertainty (weight=0.12). (3) Create claim-type entities: :policy/claim-invariant (pattern=:spec/element-type contains invariant), :policy/claim-adr (pattern=:spec/element-type contains adr), :policy/claim-negative (pattern=:spec/element-type contains negative). (4) Create evidence-type entities: :policy/evidence-witness (pattern=:witness/*, depth-mapping=L1:0.3 L2:0.6 L3:0.8 L4:1.0), :policy/evidence-impl (pattern=:impl/implements). (5) Create anomaly detectors: harvest-urgency (trigger=:tx/time, threshold=15, message=harvest overdue), witness-staleness (trigger=:witness/status contains stale), fs-regression (trigger=fitness delta < -0.05). (6) Transact at braid init alongside existing bootstrap datoms.. ACCEPTANCE: (A) After braid init, store contains 7 :policy/boundary-* entities with correct weights. (B) Weights sum to 1.0 (normalized). (C) braid query --attribute :policy/boundary-weight returns 7 datoms. (D) Existing init behavior unchanged — policy datoms are additive. (E) braid init --no-policy skips manifest (for testing empty-policy path). DEPENDS-ON: POLICY-1 (t-f5298b23). FILE: crates/braid/src/bootstrap.rs, crates/braid/src/commands/init.rs" :op :assert}
